title: World Architecture - An Illustrated History (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
World Architecture: An Illustrated History
Hamlyn | 1963 | ISBN: 0600039544 | English | 352 pages | PDF | 62.7 MB

Divided into nine chapters covering most areas on the globe,the book is well presented with B&W photographs plus plans on ancient temples or medieval cathedrals.The separate authors of the various chapters are leaders in their field from British and American universities. The number of examples is large and they are well annotated
